ğŸ“Œ 4. Installation Instructions
ğŸ”¹ 1. Clone this repository
git clone <your-repo-link>
cd ai-classroom-manager

ğŸ”¹ 2. Create & activate virtual environment
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\activate          # Windows

ğŸ”¹ 3. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

ğŸ”¹ 4. Add your API key in .env

Create a file .env inside project:

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_openrouter_key_here
AI_PROVIDER=openrouter

ğŸ“Œ 5. Running the Project
â–¶ A. Run CLI (terminal version)
python main.py


You will see:

=== AI Classroom Manager Agent (CLI) ===
1. Generate Timetable
2. Generate Lesson Plan
3. Generate Test / Worksheet
4. Parent Message
5. Behaviour Note
6. Emergency Lesson Plan
7. Progress Heatmap
0. Exit

â–¶ B. Run Flask Web App (professional UI)
python app.py


Open browser:

http://127.0.0.1:5000/

â–¶ C. Run Streamlit App (alternative UI)
streamlit run streamlit_app.py


It opens at:

http://localhost:8502/

